import React from 'react';
import { Container, Box, Button } from '@mui/material';
import Navbar from './Navbar';

const Appointments: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbar />
      <Container sx={{ mt: 5 }}>
        <Box
          sx={{
            display: 'flex',
            flexDirection: 'column',
            gap: 2,
            mt: 4,
            width: '100%',
            maxWidth: '400px',
            p: 3,
            bgcolor: '#f0f0f0', // Light grey background
            borderRadius: 2,
            boxShadow: 1,
          }}
        >
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            color="primary"
            fullWidth
            sx={{ borderRadius: '50px' }}
            onClick={() => window.location.href = '/get-appointments'} // Redirect to appointments page
          >
            Get Appointments
          </Button>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            color="primary"
            fullWidth
            sx={{ borderRadius: '50px' }}
            onClick={() => window.location.href = '/mark-prescriptions'} // Placeholder redirect
          >
            Mark Prescriptions
          </Button>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            color="primary"
            fullWidth
            sx={{ borderRadius: '50px' }}
            onClick={() => window.location.href = '/get-history'} // Placeholder redirect
          >
            Get History
          </Button>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            color="primary"
            fullWidth
            sx={{ borderRadius: '50px' }}
            onClick={() => window.location.href = '/generate-report'} // Placeholder redirect
          >
            Generate Report
          </Button>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
};

export default Appointments;
